      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys Mechanical) must hold a documented quality management system compliant with 21 CFR Part 820 or equivalent; version control and audit trail required.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under a validated installation qualified per FDA 21 CFR Part 820 QMS. Software version controlled; change log and installation qualification records archived. Achieved level meets required level."
