      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems with known analytical solutions must be solved to confirm correct implementation of governing equations for linear elastic structural mechanics.",
      "rationale": "Standard Ansys verification benchmarks (ANSYS VM1–VM10 series) executed and documented for linear elastic beam bending and contact mechanics. Results agree with analytical solutions to within 0.5%. Code verification requirement satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
